**Tailwind v4:**
- When dealing with CSS variables, use the `-(--var)` syntax instead of `-[var(--var)]`:

```tsx
export default function Component() {
  return (
    <div style={{ "--comp-color": "#ff0000" }} className="text-(--comp-color) bg-(--comp-color)/20">
      <Component2 />
    </div>
  );
}
```